title: VOTE: What Is The Best Childish Gambino Project?
text:
Home > Music > VOTE: What Is The Best Childish Gambino Project? VOTE: What Is The Best Childish Gambino Project? 0 2 Posted  37pm Gambino's discography has become increasingly eclectic over the years. 
Donald Glover was releasing music as Childish Gambino as early as 2008, and has released more than 10 projects since. His music has gone through many transformations throughout his many tapes, EPs and albums, from freestyling over Sleigh Bells, to resembling Funkadelic, who Sleigh Bells happened to sample themselves, as our "Awaken, My Love!" review points out.Gambino's projects began to transition from fun side-project to serious career move around the release of 2010's Culdesac , which is where our vote article begins. Let us know which of Gambino's varied projects is your personal favorite in the poll below, and share teh reasoning for your choice in the comments below. This should be a close one. < class="robots-nocontent" rel=""> Jan 10, 2017 at 07:37pm 193 Views
